# Lab 7 – Python Object-Oriented Programming

This project demonstrates Object-Oriented Programming concepts using a
Jujutsu Kaisen inspired character system.

## Classes

Base Class:
- Character

Child Classes:
- Sorcerer
- Curse
- Human

## OOP Concepts Demonstrated

- Inheritance
- Polymorphism (attack method overridden)
- Encapsulation (protected attribute _negativity)
- Object interaction (curses spreading fear to humans)

## Program Behavior

1. Sorcerers and curses are created.
2. A curse spreads fear to a human.
3. The human's negativity increases.
4. If negativity becomes high enough, a new curse may be created.